name: Intel Core i3-2120 2nd Gen Processor (Tray)
description: The Intel Core i3-2120 2nd Gen Processor has a Processor Base Frequency of 3.30 GHz and a 3 MB Intel Smart Cache. It has 2 cores and 4 threads. It features 2 memory channels that support DDR3 1066/1333 up to 32 GB.
